snippet.title: Zeta Wolf: First Bite | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist this cute yuri visual novel coming to Steam, May 15th 2024!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2771560/Zeta_Wolf_First_Bite/

Explore the budding friendship between Carly and Siona — two girls whose personalities couldn't be more different! Will their friendship blossom into something more? Or will their selfish desires drive a wedge between them? Find out in this lighthearted prequel to Zeta Wolf Chronicles!
